{"tid":905632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐偉康：反映國際聚焦香港自治","createTime":"2018-11-17T09:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T15:48:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a612f7137eba228d293b24c361faf9fcff7b080f","tid":905632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548107&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f50c66d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548107&h=0e4eade1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548107</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月17日 <br />\n<br />\n唐偉康：反映國際聚焦香港自治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181117/large/17la4p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F17la4p1.jpg&h=337de3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國駐港總領事唐偉康昨首度開腔回應國會報告。陳善南攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國會「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」發表報告，指北京政府持續侵蝕香港人權及法治，建議檢視軍民兩用技術出口管制政策中，將香港與中國大陸視為兩個不同關稅區的做法是否合適，事件引來社會極大迴響。美國駐港總領事唐偉康昨首度開腔回應指，有關報告值得關注，當中有關香港的部份，反映國際社會聚焦有關一國兩制及香港維持高度自治的議題。他並強調，一國兩制框架對香港保持競爭力以及美國在港利益，以至中國其他地方透過香港所得的利益都十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國商會暫不評論<br />\n<br />\n唐偉康稱，期待與香港政府就相關問題繼續保持溝通。被問到美國對港關稅政策如果有變，可能影響香港國際金融中心地位，他指出，每年國會都有不同年度報告評估中美關係，當局會繼續跟進，未有回應美國政府會否改變現行對港的貿易政策。<br />\n<br />\n香港美國商會長早泰娜（Tara Joseph）昨出席商會活動時稱，現階段仍未完全掌握會員對國會報告的意見，不便評論。從事物業管理的駐港美商仲量聯行，其國際總監（商業房地產服務）龐定勤則指，受中美貿易戰影響，內地客對外房地產投資轉為保守，近期內地資金流出有下跌趨勢，估計因美國加徵中國進口物品關稅，內地公司預期營商環境有變化，放慢投資步伐。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁銘恩  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港府反擊美指控　否認毀兩制兼卸責　 民主派轟林鄭「撩交打」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n泛民促交代馬凱事件　保皇黨反對<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民促交代馬凱事件　保皇黨反對<br />\n田北俊：23條立法越遲越辣<br />\n美領事約晤建制派不果<br />\n港府反擊美指控　否認毀兩制兼卸責民主派轟林鄭「撩交打」"},{"pid":"b794c1ca577eb40720639437da9b4603e784ab08","tid":905632,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaa1d41db869da7d1d401771badebfb2716ef86","tid":905632,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"唔知侵幾時會喺Twitter提香港呢"},{"pid":"711e0178f89c3cbc78492706cf7c113ac569377b","tid":905632,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fc2c3e95a9aa53c0cc9ecddb4a12a71826de3a","tid":905632,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abbb48a6a5d8cfc6f2ccb087360fc9f322e44b3","tid":905632,"uid":19278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b17db17814a1ba224654ef9dc7f531939a3c98","tid":905632,"uid":27723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2437ab5a85c1dde313eb9336d89d54e29cdb38f","tid":905632,"uid":13